overview: Chaos breaks out at the hospital when a mutant dumpster troll is accidentally brought to life, as a result of shoddy waste management, by the shuffle dancing young man Rasmus. Hospital Dumpster Divers is a bat shit crazy medical waste themed mini-monster splatter melted together as a practical special effects gore feast.
tagline: WASTE MANAGEMENT IS NOT A JOKE!
title: Hospital Dumpster Divers
